com.microfocus.adm.pulse.pluginapi.event

Interface PulseReviewEventPlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable, PulseEventPlugin, PulsePlugin
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PulseReviewStateChangedEventListener

    public interface PulseReviewEventPlugin
extends PulseEventPlugin

    All review event plugins should implement this interface via one of the listener sub-interfaces. It allows Pulse to identify the plugin as a review event plugin.
